

     
      "It's the best I can describe....I mean I don't sit on the council with the other big kids, but I'm not reporting directly to anyone....I even have a couple of servitors, if you can believe it. But that's nevermind."    She pulls the pipe out of her pocket and fidgets with it.  "As to that thing...the scalar manifestation is what we call it....it's a physical representation of an entwined destiny unfulfilled.  Things like that will appear to those touched by the thread.  If we can resolve the issues of fate, then we can make it disappear too."
     
    
